{"tid":790546,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"好多人每日都食唔夠飯","createTime":"2018-08-23T06:01:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T11:08:32.000Z","uid":123335,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b55491d6cad2e6287e9b5eb6c89173a2641db05f","tid":790546,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T06:01:38.000Z","msg":"世界衞生組織（WHO）和聯合國糧食及農業組織（FAO）建議，健康人士每天從碳水化合物中攝取的能量，應佔每日總能量攝取量的百分之55 至75。<span style=\"color: red;\">因此，以一個應每日攝取2000千卡的人為例，他每天需要攝取275-375克碳水化合物</span>，而攝取的最好是複合碳水化合物和天然糖。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>參考數據：</ins><br />\n飯一碗 = 50g 碳水化合物<br />\n粥一碗 = 30g 碳水化合物<br />\n<br />\n大部分香港人，早上一碗粥 = 30g <br />\n中午一碗飯 = 50g <br />\n晚餐（半）碗飯= 25g <br />\n<br />\n全日Total = 105g 碳水化合物 <br />\n（目標：275-375g，中位數 = 325g ）<br />\n<br />\n#碳水化合物赤字 = 105-325 = <span style=\"color: red;\">-220g </span><br />\n<br />\n碳水化合物不足會burn 肌肉<br />\n所以唔怪得香港男仔咁瘦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b57f0f294e5aa36354563c971bebdfe6407b19b","tid":790546,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T06:04:00.000Z","msg":"Source : <a href=\"https://www.change4health.gov.hk/tc/healthy_diet/facts/calories_nutrients/carbohydrates/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change4health.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fhealthy_diet%2Ffacts%2Fcalories_nutrients%2Fcarbohydrates%2Findex.html&d=WAyJM2esBSIt0x96w2cgd04boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=bf0e482f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.change4health.gov.hk/tc/healthy_diet/facts/calories_nutrients/carbohydrates/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"233473c7aee2d0d5e43e8ad2a8a3eb15e0556c0a","tid":790546,"uid":123335,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T06:05:17.000Z","msg":"以為食飯肥，所以唔食飯<br />\n真係on9 concept <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f278da71bcdbd4d0658511f6a354207dfd97d23","tid":790546,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T06:06:52.000Z","msg